I'm not a lawyer. What does it all MEAN?
Describing legal documents in non-legalese is fraught with potential for
misinterpretation. The actual text of the license itself is legally
binding and authoritative:
1. It allows you to freely download and use it in whole or in part for
non-commercial purposes;
2. It forbids you to redistribute any piece of it without proper attribution;